Cherami et al. v. Cantrelle et al.; and Same v. Guidroz et al. October 10, 1932.

The petition of Mr. Charles D. Breaux et al. for an extension of time within which to apply for writs of certiorari in the above entitled matters is denied. Finn v. Railroad Commission, 286 U. S. 559; Cresswell v. Tillinghast, 286 U. S. 560.
